<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-207] AsyncProducerStats is not a singleton</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-207</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;AsyncProducerStats is not a singleton. This means that if a client instantiates multiple producers, the stat is collected for only 1 instance, instead of all instances.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
